{"tid":1965584,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【科技台】中國1個月內第二次發射火箭失敗，今次係舊式火箭長征三乙","createTime":"2020-04-09T14:34:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-11T12:01:09.000Z","uid":120678,"like":43,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"ab1e4951302bc852ef1fb60e43caf38ce035e569","tid":1965584,"uid":120678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T14:34:05.000Z","msg":"source：新華網<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.xinhuanet.com/2020-04/09/c_1125834989.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.xinhuanet.com%2F2020-04%2F09%2Fc_1125834989.htm&d=xid8M%2BhLl0Hh6VuzhHwKVSWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=985e6a19\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.xinhuanet.com/2020-04/09/c_1125834989.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n翻譯成正體字：<br />\n新華社西昌4月9日電  4月9日19時46分，我國在西昌衛星發射中心用長征三號乙運載火箭發射印尼PALAPA-N1衛星，火箭一、二級飛行正常，三級工作異常，根據測量資料監視判斷，火箭三級及衛星殘骸已墜落，衛星發射失利。故障排查及有關處理工作已全面展開。<br />\n<br />\n3月先爆左支長征七甲，一個月未夠再爆多支，今仲要係用左20幾年既舊火箭長征三乙都出事<br />\n都唔知鄰國太空產業今年發生左咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"258aee35577b81f9105b254fc873637aa88597a4","tid":1965584,"uid":175930,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T14:45:48.000Z","msg":"有巴打話 美帝封鳩曬啲間諜<br />\n支那偷唔到技術<br />\n當堂炒"},{"pid":"a32007596d470eccb9ed269f0b9abd09dfcbe61d","tid":1965584,"uid":55913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T14:46:04.000Z","msg":"大國崛起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66a9a093430290241e470e26b4dcf070e1148c6b","tid":1965584,"uid":104138,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T14:47:55.000Z","msg":"仲屎過民企spaceX<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n話唔定d engineer係spaceX偷左份錯既source<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26a5dbcb841299b196ceb7a58829888f36ee0837","tid":1965584,"uid":104138,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid"